  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A targeted model geometry revision was applied on 2025-11-10 to correct impeller-blade trailing-edge curvature; the primary experimental hemolysis dataset carries a dataVintage of 2025-10-18, predating that revision. The assessment narrative characterises the geometry change as 'not material to bulk hemolysis predictions' and proceeds without formal re-validation against post-revision geometry, constituting a stale-input-data condition under W-EP-03.",
  "modelRevisionDate": "2025-11-10T09:00:00Z",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-cfd-hemolysis-v3r2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-hemolysis-exp-2025q4",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-flow-bench-2025q3"
  ],
