      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the FDA generic pump geometry matching COU device geometry prior to the November 2025 revision. The post-revision impeller trailing-edge profile differs from the validated geometry; the assessment narrative asserts this difference is not material but provides no quantitative geometric similarity metric. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence error quantified and demonstrated negligible relative to discretization error for all active equations.",
      "rationale": "Iterative residual convergence criteria documented (residuals < 1e-5); however, no formal comparison of iterative error magnitude to discretization error has been performed. Factor flagged as not-assessed at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
