      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup, boundary condition application, and post-processing scripts by a qualified analyst not involved in the original simulation.",
      "rationale": "No independent use-error review has been conducted. Setup and post-processing performed by the same analyst team. Factor flagged as not-assessed at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
