      "rationale": "Only a single pump unit used for all in-vitro hemolysis measurements; device-to-device variability not characterised. Blood analogue batch consistency not formally verified across test sessions. Factor flagged as not-assessed at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
